### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### POST INTERVIEW (Real Interview Logs)
### Base: {{baseUrl}}/real-interviews
###
### Flow:
###   1. POST /real-interviews → log questions from a real interview
###      Claude classifies each question by domain, service, difficulty
###   2. GET  /real-interviews → review all logged interviews
###
### Requires CLAUDE_API_KEY for question classification.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


### List all logged real interviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/real-interviews
Accept: application/json


###


### Log a real interview — Data Engineer at PayPal
# accountId must exist in the backend (run 02-admin.http first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/real-interviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "panelistName": "John Smith, Senior Data Engineer",
  "questions": [
    "Explain the difference between RANK and DENSE_RANK in SQL.",
    "How would you design a data pipeline that ingests 10TB of data daily?",
    "What is the difference between a data warehouse and a data lake?",
    "How does Apache Spark handle data shuffling and what are the performance implications?",
    "Describe a situation where you had to optimize a slow SQL query."
  ]
}

> {%
  client.global.set("realInterviewLogId", response.body.id);
  client.log("Logged real interview: " + response.body.id);
  client.log("Questions classified: " + response.body.questions.length);
  response.body.questions.forEach(function(q) {
    client.log("  [" + q.difficulty + "] " + q.domain + " → " + q.service + ": " + q.text.substring(0, 60));
  });
%}


###


### Log a real interview — Software Engineer at Google
POST {{baseUrl}}/real-interviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "panelistName": "Sarah Lee, Staff Engineer",
  "questions": [
    "Implement a LRU cache in Java.",
    "Explain the CAP theorem and when you would choose CP vs AP.",
    "How would you design a URL shortening service like bit.ly?",
    "What is the time complexity of merging two sorted linked lists?",
    "Explain the difference between optimistic and pessimistic locking."
  ]
}
